Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,----OP
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.99,0:00:23.21,OpeningCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}褪色的景致 隨著風兒逝去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.21,0:00:31.01,OpeningCN,,0000,0000,0000,,往日記憶 悄悄甦醒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.01,0:00:37.93,OpeningCN,,0000,0000,0000,,走在熟悉的路上卻無法回頭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.93,0:00:43.89,OpeningCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}最初的謊言 最後的話語
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.02,0:00:57.45,OpeningCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}那天許下的誓言早已崩潰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.45,0:01:04.71,OpeningCN,,0000,0000,0000,,只留下激昂虛幻的記憶碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.71,0:01:12.67,OpeningCN,,0000,0000,0000,,就算我們一同從這夢境中醒來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.67,0:01:18.89,OpeningCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}這份思念 也不會被忘記 永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.10,0:01:27.69,OpeningCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}懷念的往昔照亮今天的我
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,----ED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.64,0:22:21.86,EndingCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}那時還年幼的我 抬頭仰望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.86,0:22:28.28,EndingCN,,0000,0000,0000,,發現天空真的很遼闊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.28,0:22:32.74,EndingCN,,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡的人 用雙手保護
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.74,0:22:38.67,EndingCN,,0000,0000,0000,,我曾經認真的這樣想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.67,0:22:50.14,EndingCN,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼沒有長高 我為此而悔恨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.14,0:22:53.43,EndingCN,,0000,0000,0000,,也曾無數次伸展手臂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.43,0:23:00.81,EndingCN,,0000,0000,0000,,卻還是無法觸及 那無比寬廣的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.81,0:23:06.69,EndingCN,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我卻沒有一絲懷疑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.69,0:23:11.62,EndingCN,,0000,0000,0000,,始終堅信那美好的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.62,0:23:14.91,EndingCN,,0000,0000,0000,,也曾有過悔恨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.91,0:23:22.29,EndingCN,,0000,0000,0000,,亦會忍不住落下 大滴大滴的淚水
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.29,0:23:33.39,EndingCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}但是我堅信 那時我的眼中有著無比的光輝
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,----Dialogue
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.30,0:01:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 我上了ray=out的封面了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.30,0:01:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像做夢一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.90,0:01:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是 不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.50,0:01:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什麼 多吉哥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.60,0:01:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運動衫?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.40,0:02:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是想和我對抗麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.40,0:02:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒准這樣子也很不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.20,0:02:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者說 很帥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.40,0:02:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭頓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.60,0:02:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.80,0:02:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.60,0:02:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.60,0:02:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帥麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.50,0:02:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帥? 什麼帥?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.40,0:02:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 一起去城裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.30,0:02:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去買東西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.20,0:02:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去 我去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.70,0:02:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 這難道就是約會的邀請
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.10,0:02:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭頓說一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.30,0:02:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.30,0:02:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Glorious Brilliance
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.60,0:03:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个補陀落吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.30,0:03:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒動力是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.40,0:03:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分成很不錯 至少
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.60,0:03:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事難兩全
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.40,0:03:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 蘭頓呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.40,0:03:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭頓和優萊卡進城買東西去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.00,0:03:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.20,0:03:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為不想把他捲進這種工作裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.80,0:03:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那倒不是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.60,0:03:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是懶得跟他解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.40,0:03:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 大家都在看我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.80,0:03:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道我已經是名人了?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.70,0:03:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊 怎麼說畢竟是ray=out的封面人物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.20,0:03:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是筆記本和參考書
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.80,0:04:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學習是很重要的 好像
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.10,0:04:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.00,0:04:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭頓你平常也沒學習啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.00,0:04:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.70,0:04:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學習好的男人和成績差勁的嘔吐蟲哪個比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.80,0:04:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅特爾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.40,0:04:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭頓生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.50,0:04:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅特爾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.00,0:04:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.80,0:04:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己還不是小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.00,0:04:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.30,0:04:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你那裡長毛了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.10,0:04:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.00,0:04:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白癡 我说的当然是胳膊底下了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.00,0:04:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.90,0:04:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭小子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.60,0:04:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.30,0:04:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅特爾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.10,0:04:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅特爾不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.80,0:05:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優萊卡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.10,0:05:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也沒了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.70,0:05:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都要沒了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.80,0:05:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜 和那時候不一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.00,0:05:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…大家 大家都不回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.90,0:05:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別哭 笨蛋 別哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.80,0:05:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怕了你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.20,0:05:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓緊結束了趕快回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.40,0:05:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.50,0:05:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅特爾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.50,0:05:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅特爾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.60,0:05:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.80,0:05:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭頓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.20,0:05:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.90,0:06:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 她一定就在這附近的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.70,0:06:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許正在找我們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.60,0:06:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘔吐蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.90,0:06:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣叫著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.30,0:06:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.80,0:06:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘔吐蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.10,0:06:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.00,0:06:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅特爾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.10,0:06:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.00,0:06:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼教训她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.30,0:06:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個 因為害大家擔心了 所以應該打一巴掌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.20,0:06:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.60,0:06:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.90,0:07:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是教訓男孩的辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.40,0:07:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅特爾 你不知道你讓大家擔心了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.50,0:07:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.00,0:07:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 這孩子迷了路
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.10,0:07:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想在找到媽媽之前 暫時先領她來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.70,0:07:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是我們給您添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.40,0:07:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為表歉意 請你們喝杯茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.30,0:07:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不了 這太不好意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.70,0:07:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 梅特爾 回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.80,0:07:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我渴了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.20,0:07:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.70,0:07:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.40,0:07:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 喝了茶再走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.20,0:08:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不知道什麼叫客氣麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.80,0:08:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.00,0:08:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帽匠在茶室
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.20,0:08:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前門封住了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.20,0:08:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是白兔 前門已封住
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.50,0:08:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是紅心女王 已到達預定位置
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.90,0:08:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 愛麗絲去封後門
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.30,0:08:28.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 媽媽 這茶是紅色的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.40,0:08:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們平時喝的茶是什麼顏色的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.00,0:08:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平時岡吉泡給我們喝的是茶褐色的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.60,0:08:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.40,0:08:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麼 那麼在這裡就多放點砂糖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.40,0:08:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.40,0:08:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.10,0:09:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 好了 請吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.20,0:09:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆泡的茶 又甜又香
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.50,0:09:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像優萊卡一樣讓人覺得不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.80,0:09:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是有一點點奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.60,0:09:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我就讓你買的時候不要壓價太狠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.60,0:09:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.80,0:09:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍蘭德
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.60,0:09:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭頓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.60,0:09:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼在這兒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.40,0:09:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍蘭德才是 為什麼在這兒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.70,0:10:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這女人是叫作補陀落的反政府組織的重要人物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.30,0:10:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把她交給軍隊我們能賺錢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.20,0:10:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能這樣 月光州自己也是反政府的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.10,0:10:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了錢就什麼都做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.80,0:10:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 只要能賺錢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.70,0:10:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.70,0:10:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 把雙手放在頭上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.70,0:10:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.20,0:10:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.70,0:10:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.80,0:10:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼叫紅心女王 帽匠逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.00,0:10:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬修 快開LFO去追
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.00,0:10:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍蘭德
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.20,0:10:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別廢話 現在沒空跟你解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.80,0:11:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優萊卡 開尼爾瓦修去追
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.80,0:11:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能接受的話 你就老老實實在這兒喝茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.10,0:11:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是補陀落的考驗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.20,0:11:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.50,0:11:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.60,0:11:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑不掉了 老婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.60,0:11:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.60,0:11:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.70,0:12:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭頓 確保視野清晰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.60,0:12:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺悟吧 老婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.40,0:12:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.70,0:12:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怖分子到手了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.80,0:12:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭頓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.80,0:13:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不高興麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.30,0:13:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼能高興得起來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.90,0:13:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.60,0:13:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼在你們抓住的婆婆家裡吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.20,0:13:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道補陀落的人在想些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.50,0:13:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.40,0:13:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬修
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.00,0:13:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換蘭頓去監視老婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.80,0:13:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這家伙反正也沒心情吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.90,0:14:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次換你來幫忙了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.40,0:14:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是監視
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.60,0:14:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.80,0:14:24.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.30,0:14:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要請我們吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.50,0:14:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被抓走後這裡的食物只會白白腐爛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.50,0:14:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是食物的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.30,0:14:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是補陀落的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.70,0:14:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那邊的胡椒拿給我好麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.00,0:14:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你們抓走是我的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.20,0:14:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.60,0:14:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你剛才還是試圖逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.10,0:15:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世上既有能夠接受的命運也有應當抵抗的考驗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.90,0:15:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不大明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.90,0:15:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你不是看得見補陀落之光的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.90,0:15:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次請幫我拿辣椒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.70,0:15:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.80,0:15:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡椒邊上的那瓶就是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.10,0:15:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 你們為什麼要進行反政府運動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.50,0:15:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把鹽也拿來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.10,0:15:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們並沒有打算反抗政府
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.50,0:15:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是軍隊這樣指責我們罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.90,0:15:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把鳥關進籠子的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.40,0:15:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它會每天都夢想著天空的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.80,0:15:49.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要嘗嘗麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.50,0:15:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.00,0:16:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能你還不到吃這個的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.30,0:16:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.40,0:16:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭頓 換人了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.70,0:16:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.70,0:16:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你長大成人後 很多事情就會明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.00,0:16:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也要嘗嘗麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.10,0:16:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜歡這味道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.30,0:16:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們的靈食
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.10,0:16:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃不慣的人可能會覺得很難吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.30,0:16:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我諾魯布在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.90,0:17:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從開始就沒想要動粗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.40,0:17:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是從軍方聽說你是危險的反政府分子 很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.70,0:17:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就采取了這種精巧的做法是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.00,0:17:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.80,0:17:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底干了什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.40,0:17:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.70,0:17:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.10,0:17:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 交易完成
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.60,0:17:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.40,0:18:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 別讓他們跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.60,0:18:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.70,0:18:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.90,0:18:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 一炮解決他們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.20,0:18:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能量充填開始
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.20,0:18:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在發熱率預計數值范圍內上升
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.50,0:18:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3 2 1
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.20,0:18:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發射
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.40,0:18:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了 好極了好極了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.80,0:18:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.50,0:18:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 太帥了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.10,0:19:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帥?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.40,0:19:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 很帥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.40,0:19:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 把你捲進了我們的經濟問題中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.40,0:19:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.90,0:19:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切就如補陀落所指引
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.50,0:19:23.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是贖罪吧 我們會送你去你想去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.00,0:19:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.60,0:19:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就去我們的朝聖之地 修达德斯·德·希耶罗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.50,0:19:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起我們更重視補陀落 說明軍隊的下層還沒有收到情報吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.70,0:19:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 還不能放鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.80,0:19:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 隨著軍隊的移動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.00,0:19:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍隊內部的變動也開始活躍了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.80,0:19:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布拉波已經開始量產魂魄驅動器了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.70,0:20:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 穩健派的克萊頓將軍也遭遇了不測
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.00,0:20:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他想掌握大權啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.20,0:20:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍隊的重組麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.10,0:20:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是僅此而已就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.00,0:20:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈米的森林之王
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.20,0:20:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 大家的習題集
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.20,0:20:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 這是蘭頓的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.60,0:20:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我也要做麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.60,0:20:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才你很帥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.40,0:20:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要蘭頓一笑 尼爾瓦修就會笑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.90,0:20:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然是修达德斯·德·希耶罗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.50,0:20:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃到那難吃的饭的時候 我就有不好的預感了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.30,0:21:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那時算起 多少年了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.70,0:21:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.10,0:21:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.20,0:21:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話説回來 到底哪裡帥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.40,0:21:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.50,0:22:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事 頭好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.60,0:22:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待續
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.30,0:23:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被稱為天空之都的補陀落的聖地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.70,0:23:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡 少女的過去浮出水面
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.30,0:23:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得知了真相的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.10,0:23:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在戰火之下選擇了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.60,0:24:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 Paper Moon Shine
